= Name

[grindr] -- a xmpp message feed aggregator for superfeedr

= Synopsis

    ruby bot.rb
    # type help to <bot-jid> to get it started. (or sth else ;P)

= Description

    [grindr] is an xmpp4r bot thats listening on superfeedr's xmpp pubsub api
    and parsing it to human readable message stanzas. It provides a little
    interaction api to control the behavior of the bot.

= Install

    It's using the standard xmpp4r library and superfeedr-ruby.
    [ http://github.com/superfeedr/superfeedr-ruby/ ]
    [ http://home.gna.org/xmpp4r/ ]
    and YAML.
    install all dependencies preferably with rubygems:
        sudo gem install xmpp4r superfeedr-ruby
    Remove '.default' from config.yaml.default and edit it as you wish.

= Example

[06:05:56 AM] dodo: test
[06:05:57 AM] gringr: Welcome to gringr! You're just an unregistered Stranger. Type help for overview.
[06:05:57 AM] gringr: Yepp. I'm right here.
[06:05:58 AM] dodo: register
[06:05:59 AM] gringr: Before you're registered I want to confirm that you're a REAL self thinking organismn.
Please just answer this little question:
What is the sum of 84 and 55?
[06:06:08 AM] dodo: 139
[06:06:08 AM] gringr: Congratulations! You're now a registered user.
[06:11:02 AM] gringr: [Tue Mar 02 06:10:49 +0100 2010]   05:10:49   on [ http://superfeedr.com/?1267506649 ]
[06:11:03 AM] gringr: [200] The Dummy Time Feed
948 bytes fetched in 0.05s. Next fetch in 1m 21.28s (Tue Mar 02 06:12:24 +0100 2010).  [ http://superfeedr.com/dummy.xml ]

